==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disinterestedness
<hw>Dis*in"ter*est*ed*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality
of being disinterested; impartiality.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That perfect <qex>disinterestedness</qex> and self-devotion of
which man seems to be incapable, but which is sometimes found in
woman.</q> <rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disinteresting</ent>⟦br⟧
